Support for the SCOLD build system, which uses autotools.
But the autotools are best used with some project-specific macros and aclocal.

Building and Installing the Package

  ( ./buildconf && ./configure && make check && make install ) >& o.make.out

Building the package

  ( ./buildconf && ./configure && make ) >& o.make.out

Testing the package

  make check
  
Installing the package

  make install

